solPicker.filters
Class BaseFractionFilter

java.lang.Object
  solPicker.filters.Filter
      solPicker.filters.BaseFractionFilter

public class BaseFractionFilter
extends Filter

Calculates the percent distribution of each of the nucleotide bases, and filters oligos based on the equality of the distributions. The more uneven the distribution, the higher the base fraction score. For each base whose percent distribution is not between 25% and 35%, this filter adds one point to the base fraction score. Users can indicate a maximum score.
